                of<lb/> your people, I have<lb/> wrote two letters to<lb/>
                <add>?</add> one of them<lb/>
                <sic>resently</sic> issue I wrote<lb/> to you, for a <add>?</add><lb/> or sample of
                your <add>?</add><lb/> in the Editorial sphere<lb/> of Publications a No of the<lb/>
                Israelite a Periodical.<lb/> I have a sample of your<lb/> No. 7. It was sent to
                me<lb/> by the Ed. &amp; <sic>Propritor</sic> of the</p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p><sic>Biblicle</sic> Expositor<lb/> Printed now at <add>?</add>
                <placeName>Detr<lb/>oit Mich</placeName> I take it</p>
            <p>My Faith is in the gos<lb/>pel of our savior <persName>Jesus<lb/> Christ</persName>
                the promised<lb/> messiah the Prince of Peace;<lb/> to Reign on
                    <persName>Davids</persName> Royal<lb/> Throne or King of
                    <placeName>Israel</placeName><lb/> Personally in
                    <placeName>Jerusalem</placeName><lb/>
                <placeName><sic>Palistine</sic></placeName>, <placeName>Asia Minor</placeName>,<lb/>
                in <placeName>Turkey</placeName>. When He<lb/> comes He comes in King<lb/>dom In a
                Mighty Chariot<lb/> The city of the <placeName>New Jerusa<lb/>lem</placeName>; the
                second one.<lb/> The New Temple will<lb/> be in it and a New<lb/> Throne in it. His
                Domain<lb/> will be over the whole<lb/> earth and <add>?</add> and<lb/> seas.
                    <add>?</add> an everlasting<lb/> one as eternity.</p>
            <p>My Faith is of His Now to be<lb/> His <add>?</add> one at time of His Birth</p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p>was His first Advent. <add>?</add><lb/> Acts 1 <add>?</add> and 12 vs
                    <persName>Zach</persName><lb/>
                <add>?</add> &amp;c so likewise my Faith<lb/> is of the Restoration of the<lb/>
                whole House of <placeName>Israel</placeName> to the<lb/> hand of their Fathers
                    <add>?</add><lb/> In the days <persName>Adam</persName> it was<lb/>
                <sic>was</sic> called <placeName>Eden</placeName> Now
                    <placeName>Palis<lb/>tine</placeName>.</p>
            <p>If you will answer my<lb/> Former letter namely of<lb/> I wrote it will oblige
                me<lb/> much, or give your opin<lb/>ion on them.</p>
            <p>Return them to me after<lb/> the same manner as I<lb/> write to you not in
                man<lb/>ner as I proposed.</p>
            <p>I wish not for controversy<lb/>
                <add>?</add> in my <add>?</add> write-ing in<lb/> the way I have to you<lb/> nor for
                reputation.<lb/> I may write to you occa<add>?</add>ly<lb/> if of what I have is
                excerpted<lb/> I am a gentile and am a poor</p>
            <pb n="4"/>
            <p>and no Family &amp; live in a house<add>?</add> alone &amp;<lb/> have had a wife but
                she is<lb/> Dead and was of the same<lb/> Faith of myself she died
                <date>1850</date><lb/> what I may hereafter write<lb/> upon will be the
                    <sic>Prophecys</sic><lb/> of Holy writ, and History of<lb/> past Present and
                Future<lb/> giving my views of them<lb/> and Faith As I under<lb/>stand them they
                may be<lb/> of some importance to you<lb/> I am a professional man<lb/> a Botanic
                Doctor Reduced<lb/> by <add>?</add> of Prosperity by False<lb/> Hearted men and
                their<lb/> writing of such as Mortg<add>?</add><lb/>ages on Landed Property
                    such<add>?</add><lb/> as Real Estate.</p>
            <p>I have read two <add>?</add><lb/> of three <sic>peices</sic> of latter part of<lb/>
                the Occident and I like them<lb/> much and intend on Reading<lb/> it through.
                    <add>?</add><lb/> 18th <add>?</add>
                <persName>L. Dale. D. B.</persName><lb/> I am a man 61 years old<lb/> in 62nd
                year.</p>
